backModal_main_2529603\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104lkd1665702657821.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lkd1665702657821.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lkd1665702657821.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"lkd1665702657821\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Installable Character Sets\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"lkd1665702657821__installable_character_sets_93674\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Character sets that conform to one of several characters encoding systems can be installed into Uniface applications.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lkd1665702657821__p_d28613e1_d28614e1_d28615e1\">Before Unicode was invented, there were many character-encoding systems to provide different character set standards. For example:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lkd1665702657821__li_d14594e1_d14595e1_d14596e1\">ISO (International Standard Organization) character sets\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lkd1665702657821__li_d14597e1_d14598e1_d14599e1\">Code Pages (Microsoft character sets)\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lkd1665702657821__li_d14600e1_d14601e1_d14602e1\">National standards, such as GB for Simplified Chinese character sets, Shift-JIS for Japanese character sets\n </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lkd1665702657821__p_d28616e1_d28617e1_d28618e1\">These standards specify both the available characters and the way they are encoded, so the terms character set and character encoding are often considered synonymous. It is possible to install one of these character sets into a language-specific Uniface application. They are therefore called installable character sets.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lkd1665702657821__p_d28619e1_d28620e1_d28621e1\">When installing Uniface, you can choose to install a language-appropriate character set such as Western European, Cyrillic, or Traditional Chinese. The actual character set installed depends on the platform, operating system, and language.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lkd1665702657821__p_d28622e1_d28623e1_d28624e1\">Installable character sets can be either single-byte or double-byte. Single-byte character sets can be left-to-right, right-to-left, or bidirectional.</p>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529603\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529603\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Installable Character Sets Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Installable Character Sets Character sets that conform to one of several characters encoding systems can be installed into Uniface applications. Before Unicode was invented, there were many character-encoding systems to provide different character set standards. For example: ISO (International Standard Organization) character sets Code Pages (Microsoft character sets) National standards, such as GB for Simplified Chinese character sets, Shift-JIS for Japanese character sets These standards specify both the available characters and the way they are encoded, so the terms character set and character encoding are often considered synonymous. It is possible to install one of these character sets into a language-specific Uniface application. They are therefore called installable character sets. When installing Uniface, you can choose to install a language-appropriate character set such as Western European, Cyrillic, or Traditional Chinese. The actual character set installed depends on the platform, operating system, and language. Installable character sets can be either single-byte or double-byte. Single-byte character sets can be left-to-right, right-to-left, or bidirectional. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}